\newlabel{fig:supp-timestep}{{4}{7}{Intra-sampling HPWL change as a function of $t_{\text {start}}$, across 6 circuits and 3 seeds. Bigblue3 (the largest tractable circuit) shows a striking monotonic improvement, peaking at $-34.5\%$ HPWL. Smaller circuits show small effects, suggesting backbone-prior leverage scales with circuit size}{figure.4}{}}
